-- Evercore Partners With VTB Capital for Transactions in Russia
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2012-10-29T12:45:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-29/evercore-partners-with-vtb-capital-for-transactions-in-russia.html
Evercore Partners Inc. (EVR) , the advisory
firm founded by former U.S. Deputy Treasury Secretary Roger Altman, said it reached an agreement with VTB Capital Plc to
develop deals between Russia and North America.  “As our clients become increasingly global, it is
imperative to be able to serve their needs in important markets
throughout the world,” Ralph Schlosstein, chief executive
officer of New York-based Evercore, said today in a statement.
“This alliance is another step in the globalization of our
firm.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
